.PP
.SS "Quick start"
.PP
Connect your sensor to USB port\&. Run the launch file as:
.PP
\fC$ roslaunch adi_driver adis16470\&.launch\fP
.PP
You can see the model of ADIS16470 breakout board in rviz panel\&.
.PP
  
