.SS "ADXL345"
.PP
.SS "Overview"
.PP
  
.PP
  
.PP
The ADXL345 is a small, thin, low power, 3-axis accelerometer with high resolution (13-bit) measurement at up to ±16g\&. At this moment, support for this device is experimental\&. 
